OL,3,COnlyFans billionaire owner dies aged 43
OL,5,FThe billionaire owner of adult-content
OL,6,Fplatform OnlyFans has died after "a
OL,7,Flong battle with cancer" at the age of
OL,8,F43, the company has said.
OL,10,FLeonid Radvinsky, an American-
OL,11,FUkrainian entrepreneur, acquired the
OL,12,Fparent company of OnlyFans, Fenix
OL,13,FInternational Ltd, in 2018.
OL,15,FHe served as director and majority
OL,16,Fshareholder, and previously made
OL,17,Fheadlines in 2023 for paying himself
OL,18,Fmore than $1.3 million (about
OL,19,F#969,100) a day in dividends when the
OL,20,Fcompany made pre-tax profits of $525
OL,21,Fmillion (391.4 million).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
