OL,3,COnlyFans billionaire owner dies aged 43
OL,5,FIt became a lucrative income stream
OL,6,Ffor sex workers, celebrities and
OL,7,Finfluencers after its popularity
OL,8,Fspiked during the Covid-19 pandemic.
OL,10,FLast year Radvinsky was reported to be
OL,11,Fin talks to sell OnlyFans at a
OL,12,Fvaluation of around $8 billion (about
OL,13,F#5.9 billion).
